Summary: Took picture of buildings in Black Forest UFO on film.
trends: There have been 4 other sightings in Freiburg
There were no other sightings in Freiburg on or around February 18th 2009
divs: sighting details i am 65 and a retured police chief from illinois. on feb 18, 2009 i was on a eupopean vacation with my adult son. while driving north through the black forest of germany, my son stopped to take a picture. while driving away i took a picture through the windshield of our vehicle. upon returning to the usa i had the film developed. a ufo is clearly in the picture. enlarged to 8\10 and with low magnification you can plainly see the octagon shape of the craft. if you would like an 8\10 copy please inform me as to who and where to mail it. i will be happy to work with you as i respect your integrity. note: i did not see the object when i took the picture. sincerely yours, dennis baraks
